text: Jana Rybářová (born 13 February 1978) is a Czech synchronized swimmer. Jana competed in the women's duet at the 2000 Summer Olympics with her partner, Soňa Bernardová, and finished in fifteenth place. ==References== Category:1978 births Category:Living people Category:Czech synchronized swimmers Category:Olympic synchronized swimmers of Czech Republic Category:Synchronized swimmers at the 2000 Summer Olympics
